data.description: OPEN HOUSE Sat.12/16 1-3p Nestled on over 2 acres of picturesque countryside, this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, tranquility, and convenience. As you approach this stunning property, you'll immediately be captivated by the natural beauty that surrounds it. Towering trees and lush greenery provide a sense of seclusion and privacy, making it feel like your very own retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. This two-story home boasts a thoughtfully designed layout, featuring a spacious and inviting interior. The main floor is designed for both living space and entertaining, with a generously sized living room, a well-appointed kitchen that's a chef's delight, and a dining area that offers scenic views of the sprawling landscape. The cozy office on the main level provides the ideal space for remote work or creative pursuits. Upstairs, you'll find three comfortable bedrooms, including an owners suite complete with an en-suite bathroom
